Definition: an accusation that you are responsible for some lapse or misdeed
Example: his incrimination was based on my testimony; the police laid the blame on the driver
Synonyms: verb, stative, incriminate, communication, inculpation, inculpate, blame, cognition, accusation, an, that, you, are, responsible, for, some, lapse, or, misdeed, his, was, based, on, my, testimony, the, police, laid, driver
Category: noun.communication
